{"tid":364362,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[連登有愛] 有冇人係華富執到銀包？","createTime":"2017-08-18T10:33:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-20T23:40:23.000Z","uid":31531,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2206c9c72b40d33c31f4e9aa5f7fdec09b76e683","tid":364362,"uid":31531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T10:33:11.000Z","msg":"頭先男朋友係華富跌左銀包<br />\n位置係麥當勞附近<br />\n有冇巴絲執到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n求下你地，執到可唔可以交返俾我男朋友或者交去警署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求下你地唔好因爲少少貪念而拎左個銀包<br />\n個銀包係我男朋友生日，我第一次同佢過，第一份既生日禮物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個銀包係我特登出去上堂學整，好有意義同紀念性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入面仲有我同男朋友第一次影既貼紙相<br />\n求下你地幫幫手<br />\n我相信連登有愛架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ad503137901ab2a2671e4423ba231dd1688b5b0","tid":364362,"uid":531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T10:35:14.000Z","msg":"咁重要都可以跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"364e0a233fd7aab5119cd9c9106a6a1f19fdc4d9","tid":364362,"uid":31531,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T10:35:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/18/183456_5efbfab6b7504bf0120b03dc3c512b6f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F18%2F183456_5efbfab6b7504bf0120b03dc3c512b6f.jpg&h=f48405ae&s={SIZE}\" 